\", \\\"z\\\"}]], \\\"i\\\"]\\) \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[\\\"\
\[Sigma]\\\", RowBox[{\\\" \\\", \\\"z\\\"}]], RowBox[{\\\"i\\\", \\\"+\\\", \
