Cell["\<\
Since the local defect breaks any spatial symmetry, the only symmetry this \
model posses is the one associated with conservation of the number of magnons \
(number of spin excitations, or the number of spins up); any such symmetric \
sector may be specified: \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.985180616316884*^9, 
  3.985180698293487*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"332a07e8-2bf5-47eb-8ef1-\
